response.overview: The attractive, middle-aged owner of a trendy nightclub hires two young attractive maids to clean her house.  What they find while cleaning the bedroom leads them into a night of totally uninhabited lust.  They are invited to a party where they are the only guests and expected to provide the entertainment as well...and oh, what entertainment they provide!
response.tagline: They do more than clean the house!
response.title: Teenage Lesbian Maids
